% ============================================================================
% COURSE-SPECIFIC DEFINITIONS: ORGANIC CHEMISTRY I
% ============================================================================
% This lightweight file defines the actual named environments and symbols
% used in this specific course. It uses the semantic infrastructure from
% the base and subject-specific modules.
%
